title: Twisted Treeline ranked disabled?
body: Currently at 1:35 central time 3's map is not available for team ranked queues. Just wondering if this is intentional or not. Thanks

replies.body: Ranked teams are currently on a schedule depending on the day and time.  Check our our [ranked team schedule ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/209964886-Ranked-Teams-Schedule) guide for times for each region.  Hope that helps!
